<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:12:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官：中国对关税问题持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-china-is-open-discussion-tariffs-2024-08-01/</link><description>大众汽车首席执行官表示，中国和欧洲应该建立关税制度，奖励那些投资国内汽车生产的人，并补充说，他最近在北京会见的中国部长们愿意进行讨论，旨在寻求公平的解决方案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-china-is-open-discussion-tariffs-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>我国拟加强智能网联汽车OTA升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-plans-strengthen-intelligent-connected-vehicles-ota-upgrade-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国工信部周四发布了智能网联汽车召回和无线软件升级规则草案，旨在加强对OTA升级的监管，OTA升级在中国法规下的电动汽车产品召回中已成为常见现象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-plans-strengthen-intelligent-connected-vehicles-ota-upgrade-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>射击——中国选手刘翔夺得男子50米步枪三姿势金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-liu-wins-mens-50-metre-rifle-three-position-gold-2024-08-01/</link><description>周四，中国选手刘玉坤在巴黎奥运会男子50米步枪三项比赛中夺得金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 08:32:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-chinas-liu-wins-mens-50-metre-rifle-three-position-gold-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>随着风险回报，选举震动市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-elections-pix-2024-08-01/</link><description>委内瑞拉这场备受争议的选举是轰动一时的一年中最新的一次，世界上近一半的人将前往投票站。迄今为止的竞选提醒人们，选民仍然可以给政客和市场带来惊喜。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-elections-pix-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳回德国有关网络攻击的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-made-groundless-accusations-about-china-related-cyber-threats-says-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国驻柏林大使馆周四驳斥了德国关于北京在 2021 年对德国政府机构发起网络攻击的指控，称其为毫无根据的指控，并指责其“反华政治操纵”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-made-groundless-accusations-about-china-related-cyber-threats-says-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对中国的对冲基金配置创五年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-allocations-china-hit-five-year-low-2024-08-01/</link><description>高盛在给客户的一份报告中表示，全球对冲基金已将中国股票的敞口削减至五年来的最低水平，同时加大对日本的投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:54:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-allocations-china-hit-five-year-low-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国创下近期历史上最热月份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-records-hottest-month-recent-history-2024-08-01/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国7月份经历了现代历史上最热的一个月，这与上个月世界各地出现的创纪录的炎热天气相似。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-records-hottest-month-recent-history-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>利润率下降，中国困境打击宝马</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-auto-profit-margin-falls-short-forecast-q2-2024-08-01/</link><description>宝马周四报告称，其核心汽车业务第二季度的利润率低于预期，由于竞争加剧和中国需求疲软对该行业造成压力，该公司股价受到打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-auto-profit-margin-falls-short-forecast-q2-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车警告称，第二季度利润下降，成本削减阶段尚未结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-profit-falls-restructuring-costs-weigh-first-half-2024-08-01/</link><description>大众汽车周四警告称，其成本削减期尚未结束，并将持续到 2024 年下半年之后，因为成本上升导致第二季度营业利润下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-profit-falls-restructuring-costs-weigh-first-half-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>大型卡车制造商押注于氢气来延长内燃机寿命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/big-truckmakers-bet-hydrogen-extend-combustion-engine-life-2024-08-01/</link><description>包括沃尔沃和曼在内的一些世界上最大的卡车制造商正在改造内燃机，以使用低排放氢气而不是污染柴油，这是解决能源转型挑战的更快、低成本的解决方案，可能会给垂死的技术带来新的生命。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/big-truckmakers-bet-hydrogen-extend-combustion-engine-life-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>日本游客的挥霍行为给奢侈品牌带来了新的头痛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/tourist-splurge-japan-creates-new-headache-luxury-brands-2024-08-01/</link><description>由于日元疲软，游客纷纷涌入日本以折扣价购买高端服装和手袋。路易威登母公司路威酩轩集团等奢侈品公司宁愿他们呆在家里购物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/tourist-splurge-japan-creates-new-headache-luxury-brands-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场押注仁慈的英国央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-01/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂低迷给亚洲制造商带来压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-chinas-factory-gloom-weighs-asias-manufacturers-2024-08-01/</link><description>周四的私人调查显示，由于企业主努力应对需求不温不火的情况，中国制造业活动的低迷导致上个月亚洲工厂的表现普遍疲弱，这增加了该地区经济复苏动力不足的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 04:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-chinas-factory-gloom-weighs-asias-manufacturers-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>东京世锦赛男子和女子 100 米决赛定于第二天举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</link><description>世界田径理事会(WAC)周三表示，男子和女子100米决赛将于明年在东京举行的世界田径锦标赛第二天举行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/mens-womens-100m-finals-scheduled-day-two-tokyo-world-championships-2024-08-01/</guid></item><item><title>PMI调查增加前景风险，中国工厂准备迎接“残酷的夏天”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</link><description>中国低迷的制造业即将迎来“残酷的夏天”，本周的两项信心调查显示，因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎的工厂主的悲观情绪达到了新的水平，预示着2024年下半年经济增长面临风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:52:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-contracts-first-time-9-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>